This page on SteamDB showcases a curated list of games tagged as 'Battle Royale'. The Battle Royale tag is applied to games that adhere to the Battle Royale genre, characterized by large-scale multiplayer combat where players fight to be the last one standing. These games often feature a shrinking safe zone, scavenging for resources, and intense gunfights. The list updates automatically as new games are tagged accordingly on Steam.
